#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:4
#: b8f9509d7ff1447c98fdf89f662a74f8
msgid "开始之前"
msgstr "Before You Start"

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:6
#: 9a4122c000684d7eac36c84625fefdd4
msgid ""
"感谢你愿意为 Godot-FmodPlayer 贡献内容。无论是修文档、补示例、提交 Bug "
"复现，还是改进插件源码，都建议先花一点时间确认变更范围。"
msgstr ""
"Thank you for contributing to Godot-FmodPlayer. Whether you are fixing "
"documentation, adding examples, submitting a bug reproduction, or improving "
"the plugin source code, please take a moment to confirm the scope of the "
"change first."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:9
#: 03b3b1ddaa9d44ff9a8b94ec08f79f1d
msgid "提交前建议"
msgstr "Before Submitting"

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:11
#: ce31912afc1e4283978e60a46d298ecc
msgid "先检查现有 Issue、讨论和 Pull Request，避免重复工作。"
msgstr "Check existing Issues, discussions, and Pull Requests first to avoid duplicate work."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:12
#: 58caf5b080f24581bf4ef5ae9c1b9195
msgid "尽量让一个 Pull Request 只解决一个问题。"
msgstr "Try to keep each Pull Request focused on one problem."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:13
#: 4d40aed79d4e44fb93dcd2135dd1a3be
msgid "优先提交小而清晰的改动，避免把功能、重构、格式化和文档修改混在一起。"
msgstr "Prefer small, clear changes, and avoid mixing features, refactors, formatting, and documentation edits in one submission."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:14
#: af05d0cb0ae4402ebb5b5b42f0966582
msgid "如果修改会影响用户行为，请补充说明、示例或测试方式。"
msgstr "If the change affects user-facing behavior, add notes, examples, or verification steps."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:15
#: 3cb14a12689f4b75b28832e01659aea6
msgid "如果不确定实现方向，可以先提交草稿 PR，或在 Issue 中说明你的思路。"
msgstr "If you are unsure about the implementation direction, you can open a draft PR or describe your idea in an Issue first."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:18
#: 6dc8c45252ce4c3e81c6f1911654d8e5
msgid "适合贡献的内容"
msgstr "Good Contributions"

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:20
#: 8fdcee2c7f164eaaa4d7a25477f06f82
msgid "修正文档中的错别字、失效链接和不清楚的说明。"
msgstr "Fix typos, broken links, and unclear explanations in the documentation."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:21
#: d7d5d7858d8e4ad088648f06cf2ae62e
msgid "补充 GDScript 示例、常见用法和故障排查。"
msgstr "Add GDScript examples, common usage notes, and troubleshooting guidance."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:22
#: ad7eb57584d8452abda61f84ef574ab7
msgid "修复插件在特定平台、导出流程或音频格式上的问题。"
msgstr "Fix plugin issues on specific platforms, export flows, or audio formats."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:23
#: 064592aa640f49cab54bc49ac45f002f
msgid "改进 API 绑定、编辑器体验、导入器和总线同步逻辑。"
msgstr "Improve API bindings, editor experience, importers, and audio bus synchronization logic."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:24
#: 941536b4b2c54b77bd88503feed5c5ed
msgid "帮助维护英文翻译和术语一致性。"
msgstr "Help maintain English translations and terminology consistency."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:27
#: a69540ad8d654301b1c342df32130cbb
msgid "不建议一次性提交的内容"
msgstr "Avoid Submitting These Together"

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:29
#: 78b47d9a87e34606b3c1d568afe4fe53
msgid "大规模格式化整个仓库。"
msgstr "Large-scale formatting across the entire repository."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:30
#: 5cbc9d697b584d77a1f8e8487eb5e5b9
msgid "同时修改多个无关模块。"
msgstr "Changes to multiple unrelated modules at the same time."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:31
#: 718f4cbf96a64a4b89afae910b046dfd
msgid "没有说明原因的接口改名或行为变化。"
msgstr "API renames or behavior changes without an explanation."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:32
#: daac022849f94ef1a9e67f887a371a04
msgid "直接提交 FMOD 运行库文件。"
msgstr "Committing FMOD runtime files directly."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:34
#: 472b491541334f2d93687f117ab6d0f2
msgid ""
"FMOD Engine 受 Firelight Technologies Pty Ltd 的许可约束。插件仓库不会包含 FMOD "
"运行库，贡献时也不要把 ``fmod.dll``、``libfmod.so``、``fmod.jar`` 等文件提交到仓库。"
msgstr ""
"FMOD Engine is governed by the Firelight Technologies Pty Ltd license. The "
"plugin repository does not include FMOD runtime libraries, and contributions "
"should not commit files such as ``fmod.dll``, ``libfmod.so``, or "
"``fmod.jar``."

#: ../../source/contributing/before_you_start.rst:36
#: 7c88b44ba6204ff7800b681e1a87758a
msgid "如果你只是想先试一试，可以从文档的小修小补开始。这类改动最容易审查，也最容易帮助后来的使用者。"
msgstr "If you only want to try contributing first, start with small documentation fixes. These changes are easy to review and often very helpful for future users."
